{
  "text": "The LRT (between chi-square difference test) was \u03c7 2 = 5.35, df = 1, p = .0207, favoring the participatory practices model. A statistically significant chi-square difference test indicates that a model with a smaller chi-square statistic is a better fit of the model to the data compared to a contrasting model [CITATION_1] .",
